<br>
2 cups freshly brewed strong Coffee, any variety or brand  <br>
1 square BAKER'S Unsweetened Baking Chocolate, chopped  <br>
1/4 cup sugar  <br>
1 tsp. ground cinnamon  <br>
1-1/2 cups milk  <br>
1-1/2 tsp. vanilla  <br>
 <br>
 <br>
<br>
